Package ohos.utils.net

Class UrlQueryFilter.ValueFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.utils.net.UrlQueryFilter.ValueFilter
  • Enclosing class:
    UrlQueryFilter

    public static class UrlQueryFilter.ValueFilter
extends Object
    Represents a filter used to filter out invalid characters in a query string and replace them with spaces or underscores (_). The filtering policy uses int values to control filtering. Each bit of the int value represents whether a character in the string will be filtered out. If the value of a bit is 1, the character is valid. If the value is 0, the character is invalid and will be filtered out.
    Since:
    4
